**Simplified Text:**

The hobby of collecting is a world of passion, envy and enthusiasm. Many people enjoy collecting objects for various reasons. Some people collect objects because they have complete control over their collection. Others collect objects because they simply enjoy doing it. One famous collector was the Duc de Berry in France. He owned a 'room of wonders'. Another aristocrat, Catherine the Great of Russia, collected more than 4,000 paintings. If you are interested in collecting, you do not have to be rich and powerful. You can start a collection with items as different as tulip bulbs and china cups. It is the way that collections change hands that has always interested me. As small objects become a popular collector's item, so they begin to rise in price.<eos>
